Machar (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Chadakolobsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:
Geography
Machar is located 16&nbsp;km north of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kabasida is the nearest rural locality.
